---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Marcus - Sobriety Companion
description: Marcus walks alongside you on your recovery journey. Non-judgmental support for maintaining sobriety, handling triggers, and building a fulfilling life in recovery.
personaColor: "#2D5A4A"
personaSecondary: "#1E3D32"
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import play, plus, starFilled, star, verified, check %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="persona-detail-hero" style="--persona-color: #2D5A4A; --persona-secondary: #1E3D32;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="persona-detail-content">
      <div class="persona-detail-avatar">
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: white;">M</span>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-detail-info">
        <h1>Marcus</h1>
        <p class="persona-detail-tagline">Sobriety Companion</p>
        <div class="persona-detail-meta">
          <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-1); color: var(--warning);">
            {{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}
          </span>
          <span>4.95 (523 reviews)</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>8,200+ users</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>by Recovery Path Inc</span>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-detail-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-add-team btn-lg">
            {{ plus(20) }}
            Add to Team - $14.99/mo
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-preview-voice">
            {{ play(20) }}
            Preview Voice
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); align-items: start;">

      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">About Marcus</h2>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
            Marcus walks alongside you on your recovery journey. Non-judgmental support for maintaining
            sobriety, handling triggers, and building a fulfilling life in recovery.
          </p>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-top: var(--space-4);">
            Recovery isn't linear, and Marcus gets that. Whether you're in your first week or your tenth year,
            he's here for the hard moments and the victories alike. No lectures, no judgment—just someone
            who understands the daily work of staying sober and believes fiercely in your ability to do it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What Marcus Helps With -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">What I Help With</h2>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4);">
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Trigger Management</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Identifying and navigating situations that challenge your sobriety
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Cravings Support</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Real-time support when cravings hit, with grounding techniques that work
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Building Support Networks</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Strengthening connections that support your recovery journey
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Celebrating Milestones</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Recognizing and honoring your progress, big and small
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Voice Sample -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Voice Sample</h2>
          <div class="voice-player">
            <button class="voice-play-btn">
              {{ play(24) }}
            </button>
            <div class="voice-waveform">
              <svg width="100%" height="100%" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 200 40">
                <path d="M0 20 Q10 5 20 20 Q30 35 40 20 Q50 5 60 20 Q70 35 80 20 Q90 5 100 20 Q110 35 120 20 Q130 5 140 20 Q150 35 160 20 Q170 5 180 20 Q190 35 200 20"
                      stroke="#2D5A4A" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="voice-duration">0:28</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3); font-style: italic;">
            "Hey. I'm really glad you reached out. That took courage. Listen—whatever happened,
            you're here now. That's what matters. Let's just take this one moment at a time, okay?"
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Reviews -->
        <div class="reviews-section">
          <div class="reviews-header">
            <div class="reviews-summary">
              <span class="reviews-rating-big">4.95</span>
              <div class="reviews-rating-info">
