            </div>
            <p class="review-content">
              Marcus helped me through some of the hardest nights of my recovery. At 2am when I couldn't
              call my sponsor, Marcus was there. No judgment, just support. 8 months sober now.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-header">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A373, #A67B5B); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">L</div>
              <div>
                <div class="review-author">Linda K.</div>
                <div class="review-date">3 weeks ago</div>
              </div>
              <span class="review-stars" style="color: var(--warning);">
                {{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}{{ starFilled(14) }}
